END, [x.ProductCategory].[Name] AS [Name0], [x.ProductCategory].[Discription], [x.ProductCategory].[ParentId], [x.ProductCategory].[HomeOrder], [x.ProductCategory].[Image] AS [Image0], [x.ProductCategory].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle0], [x.ProductCategory].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias0], [x.ProductCategory].[SeoKeywords] AS [SeoKeywords0], [x.ProductCategory].[SeoDescription] AS [SeoDescription0], [x.ProductCategory].[Status] AS [Status0], [x.ProductCategory].[LanguageId] AS [LanguageId0], [x.ProductCategory].[Tags] AS [Tags0], [x.ProductCategory].[DateCreated] AS [DateCreated0], [x.ProductCategory].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [x.ProductCategory].[SortOrder], [x.ProductCategory].[HomeFlag] AS [HomeFlag0], [x.ProductCategory].[HotFlag] AS [HotFlag0], [x.ProductCategory].[NewFlag] AS [NewFlag0], [x.ProductCategory].[Id]
FROM [Products] AS [x]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [x.ProductCategory] ON [x].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory].[Id]
ORDER BY [Id1]" (0723d8ff)
